# 🥗 StayHeal

StayHeal is an intelligent food ordering platform that combines nutritional analysis, user behavior, and real-time environmental context to recommend healthier meal choices without compromising user preferences.

The recommendation engine considers nutrition, ordering history, time of day, and weather conditions to rank menu items and provide personalized health nudges.

---

## Features

- 🧠 Intelligent health scoring engine
- 🍽 Personalized meal recommendations
- 🌦 Weather-aware food suggestions
- 🕒 Time-based recommendation adjustments
- 📊 Weekly health insights
- 💡 Behavioral nudges based on order history
- ☁️ End-to-end deployment on Google Cloud Platform (Cloud Run)

