## Health Recommendation Logic

Each menu item receives a dynamic **Health Score** based on:

- Nutritional values (calories, protein, sugar)
- Recent ordering history
- Time of day
- Current weather
- Healthy eating reinforcement

Context-aware adjustments include:

- Heavy meals receive lower scores during late-night hours.
- Healthy items are boosted when recent eating habits are unhealthy.
- Comfort foods receive a slight boost during rainy weather.

