## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/recommend` | Returns ranked menu recommendations |
| POST | `/nudge` | Generates personalized behavioral nudges |
| POST | `/summary` | Produces weekly nutrition insights |

