## Local Setup

### Backend

```bash
cd backend

pip install -r requirements.txt

cp .env.example .env
# Add WEATHER_API_KEY

uvicorn main:app --reload
```

Backend runs at:

```
http://localhost:8000
```

### Frontend

Open:

```
frontend/index.html
```

Update `API_BASE_URL` in `frontend/app.js` if required.

---

## Deployment

The application is containerized with Docker and deployed on **Google Cloud Platform**.

Deployment workflow:

```
Local Development
        │
        ▼
Docker Image
        │
        ▼
Google Cloud Build
        │
        ▼
Google Cloud Run
```

Deploy using:

```bash
gcloud builds submit \
  --config cloudbuild.yaml \
  --substitutions=_WEATHER_API_KEY="YOUR_API_KEY"
```

